{"tid":1159391,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"2NE1 10週年合體！終於唱《GOODBYE》　難過望Minzy：那時妳不在","createTime":"2019-05-17T15:55:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-18T13:24:39.000Z","uid":74065,"like":54,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"25de87603810eaa46c67bfafa7e88c42570af1d9","tid":1159391,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T15:55:22.000Z","msg":"南韓女團2NE1為樂壇掀起一陣girl crush風，她們唱紅多首動感夯曲，獨樹一幟的風格圈粉無數，怎料，團體在2016年宣布解散，令大批歌迷震驚不已。3年來，她們時常私下聚會，感情不變，但從未4人再度合體，5月17日這天正是團體出道10週年，Bom、Dara、CL、Minzy竟同時到場開直播祝賀，齊聲喊著口號，令歌迷淚流滿面。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4102/d4102625.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4102%2Fd4102625.jpg&h=e22dc828&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲2NE1自解散以來，首度4人重聚。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<br />\n2NE1自解散以來，成員依舊常常私約，但經常3缺1，鮮少有到齊的時刻。5月17日適逢團體10週年，Bom、Dara、CL、Minzy竟同時到場，她們開啟直播歡慶這一刻，合體喊口號「What's up! We are 2NE1」，CL率先開口：「Black Jack們，好想你們。」勾起歌迷滿滿回憶。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4102/d4102628.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4102%2Fd4102628.jpg&h=7928ddf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼2NE1同時開啟，直播在歡笑聲度過。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4102/d4102627.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4102%2Fd4102627.jpg&h=a008cf55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4人精心準備蛋糕，唱著祝2NE1 10週年快樂，回憶10年來的點點滴滴，CL爆料曾在日本跑行程時，因為要連續進行宣傳活動，舞台服裝必須統一，衣服曾經超過好幾天沒洗，回想起過去，她們臉上滿滿笑容，她還加碼糗：「姊姊愛碎念的個性都沒變！」瞬間充滿笑聲。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4102/d4102626.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4102%2Fd4102626.jpg&h=6ca2cfcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲2NE1身為大勢女團，2016年卻無預警解散。（圖／翻攝自IG）<br />\n<br />\n直播進行將近40分鐘，當接近尾聲時，CL為朴春、Minzy的solo活動以及Dara在綜藝活躍的表現應援，朴春立刻給予支持：「CL你也要回歸啊！」她看向對方回答：「我嗎？我當然也要。」她感性表示：「我們度過很愉快的時光，真的隔了很久。」向歌迷表達感謝，並透露大家都過得很好，藉著10週年的機會與粉絲見面，未來都會朝著目標繼續努力，Dara最後哼了幾句《GOODBYE》，成員卻突然悲從中來望向Minzy：「妳那時不在&hellip;」，但她們隨即展換心情，笑著與粉絲道別。<br />\n<br />\n時代既眼淚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d76c5789831e5b3a12b6634c998956c8321e3f","tid":1159391,"uid":138138,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T16:02:50.000Z","msg":"垃圾楊菊花"},{"pid":"4a580c83198cf873767f1098e6ca6e6c1f83828f","tid":1159391,"uid":74065,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e0d76c5789831e5b3a12b6634c998956c8321e3f","tid":1159391,"uid":138138,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T16:02:50.000Z","msg":"垃圾楊菊花"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T16:04:37.000Z","msg":"就快可以走"},{"pid":"5ff20e6bf11c5c1e1276de1cce61e5a942805244","tid":1159391,"uid":138138,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"4a580c83198cf873767f1098e6ca6e6c1f83828f","tid":1159391,"uid":74065,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e0d76c5789831e5b3a12b6634c998956c8321e3f","tid":1159391,"uid":138138,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T16:02:50.000Z","msg":"垃圾楊菊花"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T16:04:37.000Z","msg":"就快可以走"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T16:10:43.000Z","msg":"偏心bp都算<br />\n續完約之後雪cl係咩玩法？<br />\n次次預告定話邊隊邊隊準備緊<br />\n一年後繼續影都無，永遠得過吹字<br />\n <br />\n垃圾公司好快玩完"},{"pid":"2797d25a848e434a720b4ee30689447a6aed0638","tid":1159391,"uid":79442,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T16:19:18.000Z","msg":"唔係不和咩個陣"},{"pid":"916bcc7b8383985029f41d9ea0a8fc19e71ab852","tid":1159391,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T17:48:25.000Z","msg":"無LINK?"},{"pid":"465e2bf7ae012365f23284634ae8f5a900f43d95","tid":1159391,"uid":26773,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T17:49:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=phGur4M9ics\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yout